:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"E-Commerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1109314\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:319:\"Our advanced apologies if you were expecting a romantic date with one of the team… this tutorial is all about how you can make more money as an e-commerce business during this season. Valentine’s day is only one day and for many retailers, this can be very stressful as much emotion surrounds this day and [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Ronald\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11705:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Our advanced apologies if you were expecting a romantic date with one of the team… this tutorial is all about how you can make more money as an e-commerce business during this season. Valentine’s day is only one day and for many retailers, this can be very stressful as much emotion surrounds this day and the customer wants it to be absolutely perfect. It is not uncommon that a business is planning a great offer throughout January, but as the day gets nearer, panic rises as there&#8217;s lots of detail on how to fulfil orders and deliver them on time. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We’ll be using the example of a Flower shop to see how to better manage customer expectations, as well as increasing your revenue through upselling, better organisation and expanding your services and products including:</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Adding a personal message to gifts</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Adding a gift card or experience </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Upselling a box of Chocolates</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Setting a delivery date for Valentine’s day</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Manage your orders with a custom order status</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Don’t lose shoppers with an ‘easy login’ reminder</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>1) Adding a personal message</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Do you have a shop that sells personalized gifts and struggles to get the right details sent or charge the right amount? If that is the case, let us introduce the <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/\">YITH WooCommerce Product Add-ons</a> plugin to you. It has the ability to add anything to a product, whether this is a name to be engraved, a personal message or a photo that needs to be uploaded, as well as many more options. You can even charge a fee per letter. But for the sake of the Flower shop example, let’s keep it simple. Customers are able to add an additional card to be attached to a bunch of flowers with a personal message. No more phoning, emails and matching the message with an order, it is straight there with the actual order.</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109656\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/add-message.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Here is how the customer can add a personal message to an order</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>2) Selling Gift Cards</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Apart from selling gift cards of your own shop and products, you could collaborate with neighbouring or complementing businesses. Let&#8217;s imagine your next-door shop is a beauty salon, you could agree to sell their services for a commission and they could do the same on your products.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\">YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a> allows you to create your own designs or set the value against products. An easy way to upgrade or sell something for the undecided customer that has to buy something.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">By adding an additional service or product, you can now get the customer to buy the whole experience through you instead of the customers having to go to different shops. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With Gift Cards, you can set a date for the delivery, so getting that purchase from a customer early has never been easier.</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109452\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/giftcar-buying.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"485\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Here is an example of what the Gift Card buying experience looks like</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>3) Upselling chocolates</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A hard-to-resist deal like a box of chocolates at 50% off, when spending a minimum amount, can greatly increase revenue. Not only do you encourage the customer to spend more, but also sell another item while the customer feels good getting this special deal. With <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-deals/\">YITH Deals for WooCommerce</a> you can set these rules, so for example, if a customer buys the standard bunch of flowers, I can now prompt the customer to upgrade and get a box of chocolate at 50% off. All, with one single prompt at the moment when they are most likely to convert.</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109451\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Upsell_chocolates.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"627\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Doubling your revenue &#8211; the popup deal to upsell a box of chocolates</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>4) Setting Delivery Dates</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Not every item you sell has to be delivered on Valentine&#8217;s day, but if it is, you&#8217;d rather know in advance. Even more important is when you have a limited number of delivery drivers and each can only deliver 10 bunches per hour. You certainly would want to limit this and be able to sleep at night in the run-up to Valentine’s day. Giving the option of a delivery date is the easiest way to manage this. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-delivery-date/\">YITH WooCommerce Delivery Date</a> can be installed and set up within minutes.</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109458\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25.png 1796w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-300x160.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-1024x545.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-768x409.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-1536x818.png 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-261x139.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-311x166.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-363x193.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screenshot-2020-01-28-at-14.35.25-270x144.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The delivery date and available time-slots can be set at the checkout</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>5) Custom Order status</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-custom-order-status-subscription/\">YITH WooCommerce Custom Order Status</a>, you can create different statuses’ for your orders. This is particularly useful when you have orders that need another step in the process. In our first example, when adding custom messages or ‘names’ for engraving, you can create an order status of ‘customisation’. Or if you have many orders that need processing a day before Valentine’s day, you can give these orders a custom status. There are so many more reasons why you would want to change the status of an order and this can really help to keep track of them at every stage, and also by all the staff processing them. On top of that, each status can trigger an email to notify the customer of the process. </span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1109450\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/custom-order-status-e1580287924303.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"355\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Different types of order status’ &#8211; each status can trigger a follow-up action.</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><b>6) Easy Login and Registration</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Streamlining the buying process is always a hot topic. A user-friendly website has obvious benefits for both parties, but with the new <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-easy-login-register-popup-for-woocommerce/\">WooCommerce Easy Login &amp; Register</a> plugin, we have noticed another trend&#8230;  Impulse purchases are mostly bought on mobile devices and whilst performing another task, like watching TV, travelling or being at work. This often results in a high &#8216;abandoned cart&#8217; rate, maybe to keep the purchase a surprise for a loved one, or generally when the buying process is disturbed due to other external influences. There are so many reasons why people abandon their cart and it is never a bad idea to remind them about it later on. With <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-easy-login-register-popup-for-woocommerce/\">WooCommerce Easy Login &amp; Register</a> popup reminder, we have made the login and registration a whole lot easier. This is a completely new plugin that, when coupled to an abandoned cart reminder plugin, or external service like MailChimp, you will see the conversion rate increase dramatically.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109448\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Easy-login.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"555\" /></p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Easy Login for WooCommerce in action with an easy way to login or register.</span></i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With just one of these six plugins, you can greatly streamline both the buying process and administration of your WooCommerce store, nevermind the growth in revenue from increased sales and improved customer service.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With all YITH plugins, you can test these on a sandbox site with all the premium settings. Even better is that you can enable other plugins to see how they complement each other. </span></p>\n<h3>The Complete Toolkit</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress with WooCommerce</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/\">YITH WooCommerce Product Add-on</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\">YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-deals/\">YITH Deals for WooCommerce</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-delivery-date/\">YITH WooCommerce Delivery Date</a> </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-custom-order-status/\">YITH WooCommerce Custom Order Status</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-easy-login-register-popup-for-woocommerce/\">YITH WooCommerce Easy Login &amp; Register</a></span> with <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-recover-abandoned-cart/\">YITH WooCommerce Abandoned Cart</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Joining the <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/membership/annual-yithemes-club-subscription/\">YITH Club</a> will give you instant access to all of our plugins.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:108:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/e-commerce/level-up-your-store-with-yith-make-the-most-out-of-valentines-day/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"WordCamp Zaragoza 2020: Second year as sponsors in the capital of Aragon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:105:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-zaragoza-2020-second-year-as-sponsors-in-the-capital-of-aragon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:113:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-zaragoza-2020-second-year-as-sponsors-in-the-capital-of-aragon/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 16:07:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1108920\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:322:\"Another WordCamp for the resume of our company! Although the second time we visited and joined forces with WordCamp Zaragoza, the energy we received was a whole new experience for us! Of course we could not wait to share some of the best moments of yet another WordCamp, located in the north of Spain. WordPress, [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Athena\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7573:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another WordCamp for the resume of our company! Although the second time we visited and joined forces with WordCamp Zaragoza, the energy we received was a whole new experience for us! Of course we could not wait to share some of the best moments of yet another WordCamp, located in the north of Spain. WordPress, culture and icy feet! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f601.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We arrived a freezing cold Friday evening after a long trip from our velvet canarian climate, to an iron steel temperature drop! It was such a great experience travelling by train and looking around the picturesque winter scenery of Spain. Attending WordCamps has been such a privilege for us, as we get the opportunity to collect beautiful pictures and moments, doing what we’re most passionate about, all at once! Arriving at the speakers&#8217; and sponsors&#8217; dinner was the perfect ending to a tiring but nonetheless rewarding day! We couldn’t miss it for the world! Wine or beer to warm up the heart and nose and some delicious, gourmet bites were served making us feel right at home. We were pleased to see old friends, meet new ones and set the scene for tomorrow’s big day. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1108928 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-300x139.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-768x355.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-261x121.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-311x144.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-363x168.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/01-270x125.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Waking up was quite a challenge but arriving at ETOPIA Centro de Arte Y Tecnología was the best remedy. A space so unique but at the same time suitable for hosting a WordCamp event. We firmly believe that web designing is so deeply connected to the arts, and our community is here to prove that by spreading the ideas of WordPress in an art gallery!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1108922 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-300x139.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-768x355.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-261x121.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-311x144.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-363x168.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02-270x125.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We set our stand with our famous t-shirts and stickers and it didn’t take too long until the first WordPressers entered ETOPIA! The crowd was vivid and friendly as many attendees passed by to talk or ask about us. Soon half of our t-shirts had been given away! An absolute blast! </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1108923 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-300x139.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-768x355.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-261x121.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-311x144.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-363x168.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/03-270x125.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another active crowd was the one of the speakers, contributing with at least 38 talks!! Our developer Francisco Mendoza participated too, telling us about the role of Cron Jobs. </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1108924 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-300x79.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-768x203.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-261x69.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-311x82.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-363x96.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/04-270x71.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Closing an amazing day, our good friend José Ramón Padrón, presented his <b>10 reasons for which you need to go to WordCamp Europe Porto 2020,</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> making an introduction on the biggest WordCamp event of the world, leaving us with a great sense of what’s yet to see and experience!! We cannot wait to share more moments in our blog and each time realise even more the meaning and power of the WordPress community!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1108925 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-300x139.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-768x355.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-261x121.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-311x144.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-363x168.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/05-270x125.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Apart from WC Europe, we will be sponsoring and participating in more events during 2020. We are excited to mention the ones we will be attending! Don’t hesitate to stop by and meet us in these upcoming events:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.chiclana.wordcamp.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WordCamp Chiclana</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.laspalmasgc.wordcamp.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WordCamp Las Palmas</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.dc.wordcamp.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WordCamp Washington DC</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.torino.wordcamp.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WordCamp Torino </span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.madrid.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp Madrid</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.irun.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp Irun</a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://2020.europe.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp Europe Porto</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:110:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-zaragoza-2020-second-year-as-sponsors-in-the-capital-of-aragon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"Sponsoring Twenty WordCamps; a recap of an extraordinary year.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/sponsoring-twenty-wordcamps-2019/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/sponsoring-twenty-wordcamps-2019/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 19 Dec 2019 12:05:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1102458\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:282:\"We did it, we broke our record of the number of WordCamps we visited in 2019 from 17 the previous year. In total, we attended 20 WordCamps. Each of these events had at least one of the YITH crew attending, if not as a speaker, or is it as part of the organising team. Many [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Ronald\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41370:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We did it, we broke our record of the number of WordCamps we visited in 2019 from 17 the previous year. In total, we attended 20 WordCamps. Each of these events had at least one of the YITH crew attending, if not as a speaker, or is it as part of the organising team. Many held contributor days, which we mostly attended too.<br />\nWe must have met with over 9000 dedicated WordPressers through these 20 WordCamps. Many more through other events including Meetups and marketing events. We printed thousands of t-shirts of various iconic designs that included texts: &#8220;I survived Gutenberg&#8221; and &#8220;Keep Calm and Clear Cache&#8221;&#8230;and not one is left in our storage. What a success they have been!</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What is a WordCamp?</span></h2>\n<p>There is a good chance you have not been to a WordCamp before but surely have heard it mentioned on many occasions. In a nutshell, it is a WordPress conference organised by WordPress enthusiasts for mainly local WordPress users of any background and skill. Often it consists of one or two conference days with various talks on many WordPress and business-related subjects plus a contributor day. A contributor day is a way to support make.wordpress.org help improve the open-source software we all love to use. This can be done on many different ways from code, translation, support and marketing. Read more about <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/what-it-means-to-contribute-to-wordpress/\">&#8216;what it means to contribute to WordPress&#8217;</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Here are the twenty WordCamps we visited in 2019</span></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1 &#8211; WordCamp Zaragoza</span></h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1103577\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1103577\" style=\"width: 1155px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1103577\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Zaragoza Attendees\" width=\"1155\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-300x86.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-768x220.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-261x75.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-311x89.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-363x104.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WordCampZaragoza-e1576670508323-270x77.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1103577\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Credit: WordCamp Zaragoza 2019</figcaption></figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This was first WordCamp of the year held in January 2019 in Spain and how to better kickstart this year by Nando, our CEO, for being one of the speakers. Also, Carlos Rodriguez and Francesco Mendoza attended this event and represented YITH. Carlos and Francesco M are by now pretty familiar faces within the Spanish WordPress community. <a href=\"https://2019.zaragoza.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp Zaragoza</a> </span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/francisco-mendoza.jpg\" alt=\"Francesco Mendoza\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Francesco Mendoza</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“It is now a regular WordCamp in our calendar. The atmosphere and dedicated organisers plus the enthusiastic attendees made it a real joy to attend. We are planning to visit Zaragoza again in 2020. Hope to see you there again.”</span></i>             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2 &#8211; WordCamp Las Palmas</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Help over two iconic locations on 8 &#8211; 9 February 2019. Both Carlos and Francesco loved meeting the WordPressers from this Gran Canarian Island. Also, Nando our CEO, was one of the speakers at this event. Read more about last years event<a href=\"https://2019.laspalmasgc.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> here.</a></span></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1103151\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1103151\" style=\"width: 1155px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1103151\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"229\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-300x59.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-768x152.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-261x52.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-311x62.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-363x72.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LasPalmasWC-270x53.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1103151\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Attendees of WordCamp Las Palmas. Can you spot the green YITH shirts?</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">3 &#8211; WordCamp Torino</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1037293\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Torino 2019\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cover-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Francesco Licandro and Francesco Leanza represented YITH in Torino. Also our CEO Nando Pappalardo made an appearance as one of the speakers. Some of the most memorable activities included board games, ping-pong, table football, karaoke… Yes, it&#8217;s not always about WordPress but also hanging out with friends and making new ones.  <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/\">Read the blog here</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/francesco-licandro-2.jpg\" alt=\"Francesco Licandro\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Francesco Licandro</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				&#8220;Keep calm and clear cache” won all people approaching the booth, they couldn’t help asking for one! Some of them use to collect all our t-shirts and could not absolutely miss this new piece.             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">4 &#8211; WordCamp Madrid</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In total four of our crew attended WordCamp Madrid consisting of Carlos R, Anke, Francesco M and Kevin. A stunning and iconic location and the plan is to make this a key event for YITH in 2020 again. Read more about WordCamp Madrid <a href=\"https://2019.madrid.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here.</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/carlos-rodriguez.jpg\" alt=\"Carlos Rodriguez\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Carlos Rodriguez</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				Madrid is one of the best WordCamps I have attended. The place was spectacular and the type of talks were great. In particular the lightning talks (10 min) and the workshops. Madrid makes you feel the power of the community. Each year it gets better! Of course, next year I will try to be there.             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">5 &#8211; WordCamp London</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1036210\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog-1000-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ronald.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ronald Gijsel</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“This was my first WordCamp for YITH as the new Brand Ambassador. I had been to a few WordCamps before in London. With over 600 attendees it had a real international feel to it. I also spoke at the event about the lifecycle of a post… It was, therefore, a first for speaking too. I am sure we will be back in London for 2020”</span></i>             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/keep-calm-and-clear-your-cache-wordcamp-london-2019/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the blog here </span></a></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">6 &#8211; WordCamp Bilbao</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Our regular Spanish WordCamp crew, Carlos Rodriguez and Carlos Mora attended WordCamp Bilbao at the Maritime Museum. Furthermore, Fernando who is now YITH&#8217;s project and Marketing manager, spoke at the event. The subject was about Analytics and what it can bring you to any web project. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">7 &#8211; WordCamp Bari</span></h2>\n<p>Already on the second edition of this WordCamp in Southern Italy, <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Francesco Grasso and Corrado Porzio attended this superbly organised event. 21 speakers shared their knowledge on 18th May 2019.</span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/francesco-grasso.jpg\" alt=\"Francesco Grasso\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Francesco Grasso</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				&#8220;Speaker at a WordCamp&#8230; was not the first experience for me, but I can confirm that it&#8217;s always an emotion. In Bari I found an audience very interested in what I was saying and there was so much interaction during the talk. What about the organization&#8230; I come from Sicily, so between me and the organizers there is a lot of empathy and a sense of belonging to the territory. It was like spending a weekend with distant relatives, a sense of family that is difficult to replicate. Francesco Cozzi and Francesco Di Candia, but also the rest of the organizing team, have made the &#8220;Baresi days&#8221; an excellent opportunity for networking and community.&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">8 &#8211; WordCamp Bristol</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1050057\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blog-1000-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ronald.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ronald Gijsel</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“Bristol is close to my heart as it was my first regular meetup I attended and this year was my second time as a co-organiser. During the WordCamp, I represented YITH as the Brand Ambassador and met with many regular and local attendees. A totally different vibe to London and super amazing to be part of”</span></i>              </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div> <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/its-the-community-that-made-wordcamp-bristol-truly-amazing/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the blog here</span></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">9 &#8211; WordCamp Irún</span></h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1103382\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1103382\" style=\"width: 1155px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1103382\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-300x113.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-768x290.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-261x98.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-311x117.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-363x137.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Webp.net-resizeimage-e1576589971182-270x102.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1103382\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image: WordCamp Irun &#8211; Easy to spot the iconic green polo shirts.</figcaption></figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Carlos Rodriguez and Francisco Mendoza flew the flag for YITH at another highly successful WordCamp.</span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/francisco-mendoza.jpg\" alt=\"Francesco Mendoza\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Francesco Mendoza</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;WordCamp Ir<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ú</span>n has been a real joy to attend and sponsor. We also enjoyed a lot the Irún gastronomy, where we eating a lot of &#8220;pintxos&#8221; and also, drinking some &#8220;Kalimotxos. Another thing that really stood out was the &#8216;street event&#8217; on the first day with the 5 free talks. The organisers did themselves and the town really proud. It looks like the event is going to be repeated and we&#8217;d love to attend again in 2020&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">10 &#8211; WordCamp Europe &#8211; Berlin</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1063063\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/blog-w1000_berlino-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p>This was the wonderful location that hosted WordCamp Europe 2019, with <strong>2734 actual participants (3260 sold tickets)</strong> and an awesome team that put on this event.</p>\n<p>The venue, the Estrel Hotel, was big enough to welcome the biggest number of attendees ever in a WordCamp, and still not too big to get lost. <strong>Simply perfect</strong>. This made it easy for attendees to enjoy the event and move between tracks, from a speech to the other, and visit the sponsors area and the lunch area. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-europe-2019-berlin-in-our-hearts/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the blog here</span></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This year&#8217;s WCEU was attended by Giuseppe, Ausilia and Francesco G.</span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/ausilia-150.jpg\" alt=\"Ausilia\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ausilia</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“I think WordCamp Europe is an extraordinary experience, it’s a big event and a great opportunity to get in touch with members of the WordPress community other than the Italian one, it gives you a broader idea of what WordPress universe is, how heterogeneous and inclusive it is. It is always exciting to join an event like this year after year.”</span></i>              </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">11 &#8211; WordCamp Brighton</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1072219\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/blog-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As usually goes within the UK, Ronald attends his local WordCamps due to the location. Sun, Sea, WordPress and yes, also a bit of rain&#8230; but essentially all went well and &#8216;relax&#8217; was the most used word to describe this WordCamp. </span><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/relax-we-were-at-wordcamp-brighton/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the full blog here</span></a></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ronald.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ronald Gijsel</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Brighton is ‘down the road’ from London with a unique WordPress community. There is a beach, a great city centre for going out and some great people… however, I remember the rain the most. After all, it is Britain in August and anything can happen… and so it did. Someone got the glitter out at the Saturday social and all WordPressers ended up with glitter on their heads. Did this really happen? I can’t wait for 2020&#8230;”</span>             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">12 &#8211; WordCamp New York</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1081161\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-design-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ronald crossed &#8216;the pond&#8217; to attend WordCamp NYC. This is not the first time we went to attend a WordCamp in the USA, but certainly for New York. Only a stone throw away from Times Square, the Convene was just the perfect location. The conference rooms, hallway track and the food served was superb. The range of attendees speakers and fellow sponsors will certainly help in convincing us to return next year. </span><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/when-yith-visited-the-big-apple-wordcamp-new-york-city/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the blog here</span></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">13 &#8211; WordCamp Nijmegen</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1082306\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header.png\" alt=\"WordCamp Nijmegen\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header.png 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-300x84.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-768x215.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-261x73.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-311x87.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-363x102.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Copy-of-YITH-header-270x76.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p>In its third year, WordCamp Nijmegen obviously enjoyed a wealth of experience in the organisation of a WordCamp. The team really put up a good show! The location was ROC Nijmegen which is a professional education centre where youngster train for all sorts of jobs in a real-life environment. WordCamp Nijmegen partnered with ROC, and with the help of students they set up a perfect WordCamp environment. A great format that hopefully is copied a lot more. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/we-attended-wordcamp-nijmegen/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read the blog here</span></a></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ronald.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ronald Gijsel</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;It was one of the most intensive WordCamp days and by the time I arrived home, I was tired but satisfied. A quick flick through twitter and I think pretty much everyone agreed with me too who attended #WCNMGN&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">14 &#8211; WordCamp Catania</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1084125\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/cover-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This was a special WordCamp for all of us at YITH, as it was organized in the city where YITH took its first steps and where one of the two YITH offices is located. Without detracting from the efforts and support we put into all the other WordCamps, in which we are eager to take part every time, Catania meant something more to us, as it’s part of our hearts, our roots. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-catania-2019-simply-in-our-heart/\">Read the blog here</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/anke.jpg\" alt=\"Anke\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Anke</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;Although Italian isn&#8217;t my first language, I have to say that I&#8217;ve enjoyed the speeches I’ve attended and the overall Italian hospitality.&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">15 &#8211; WordCamp Verona</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1088356\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/blog_1000-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With Nando Pappalardo as a speaker and two crew including</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Marco Salvo and Alessio Torrisi we ascended into the beautiful city of Verona. If William Shakespeare made Romeo and Juliet (<em>Romeo and Giulietta</em> in Italian) the symbol of the city, today the <em>WordPress community replies with Wapeo and Wapetta</em>, the tender mascots of WordCamp Verona. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-verona-2019-the-wordpress-family-in-the-city-of-romeo-and-juliet/\">Read the blog here</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/marco-salvo.jpg\" alt=\"Marco Salvo\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Marco Salvo</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;I had so much fun and I had the opportunity to understand the spirit behind the community, which is not just a wonderful family, but it’s full of professionals too.</p>\n<p>From this WordCamp I’m taking away the energy and the will of sharing that you can hardly find in other similar events.&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">16 &#8211; WordCamp Dublin</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1091058\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header.png 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-300x84.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-768x215.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-261x73.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-311x87.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-363x102.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Dublin-YITH-header-270x76.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Dublin WordCamp is held every two years as it alternated between Belfast. For YITH this was the first WordCamp in Ireland and we had the honour to sponsor it too. We particularly felt appreciated by the team and attendees which made me, and the rest of the YITH team, feel really special. Read on about my experience of attending WordCamp Dublin as the YITH brand ambassador. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/when-yith-went-to-ireland-to-attend-wordcamp-dublin/\">Read the blog here </a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">17 &#8211; WordCamp Valencia</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1090158\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured.jpg 1155w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-1024x286.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-1000x280.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/featured-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This year seems to be following through in a very unique way for our company, taking us to first time events and experiences, and opening a new path for the new year’s achievements and resolutions!<br />\nOne of these events was WordCamp Valencia! First time to sponsor and attend this vibrant WordCamp, all we are left with is a big smile and a warm heart! Read Carlos&#8217; and Athena&#8217;s experience<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-valencia-2019-the-green-t-shirt-in-new-adventures/\"> in the blog here</a> </span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/athena-kiourka.jpg\" alt=\"Athena\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Athena</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;The YITH stand quickly emptied and we couldn’t be more grateful for the support of all the people that approached us in such a friendly way, asking about us and our products. The participants together with the excellent job the volunteers offered, filled the room with a vibe of unity and solidarity. &#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">18 &#8211; WordCamp US</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1095453\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-768x215.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/featured_WCUS-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p>As one of the biggest global WordCamps, the US didn’t disappoint to the 1500 attendees. A huge international presence descended onto the Mississippi CIty of St Louis. Also, YITH was one of the many companies that represented a part of this wonderful global WordPress community. We sent Ronald, our brand ambassador to represent YITH. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/yith-sponsored-wordcamp-us-2019-at-the-american-centre-in-st-louis/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Read Ronald&#8217;s blog here</span></a></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ronald.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Ronald Gijsel</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;Looking back a couple of weeks since WordCamp US, I still feel a bit of a buzz around the whole event. So many people spoken with, new impressions, improved friendships and lots of information to process. Reading many other WCUS blogs, I am certainly not the only one.&#8221;             </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">19 &#8211; WordCamp Milano</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1101427\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Milano 2019\" width=\"1155\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo.jpg 1152w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-1024x288.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-768x216.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/milano_testata-articolo-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">22-23 November 2019: we end our Italian WordCamps marathon with a bang, with a stop-over in Milan. Alberto Ruggiero, Marco Salvo and Alessio Torrisi had the immense pleasure to represent YITH <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-milano-2019/\">&#8211; read the blog here</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/ALESSIO-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alessio Torrisi\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Alessio Torrisi</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;This was our 12th WordCamp, but each of them is different: you always meet someone new and they all leave their mark.</p>\n<p>The best memory I brought back home from WordCamp Milan is the <strong><em>touching speech by Mauricio Gelves about Carla Saiz&#8217;s story</em>.</strong></p>\n<p>Knowing that the WordPress community stood by this girl to support her and help her is just amazing!<strong>&#8220;</strong></p>\n<p>            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">20 &#8211; WordCamp Granada</span></h2>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1101321\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo.jpg 1152w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-1024x288.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-768x216.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/testata-articolo-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1155px) 100vw, 1155px\" /></p>\n<p>We have to confess that thanks to the WordCamps we’re sponsoring, we are literally falling in love with Spain and all its wonderful cities.</p>\n<p>This weekend, we attended WordCamp Granada 2019 and now we must inevitably list this city among the top ten places worth visiting at least once in a lifetime: maybe it’s somewhat cold for us, as we’re used to Tenerife’s temperatures, but it’s a fascinating city, with its Arab history and the Sierra Nevada that rises majestically elegant on the horizon.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Se sent Ivan and Francisco M, who presented a workshop on how to use WooCommerce. And to finish with a cherry on top, Sara Presenti did a talk about Emotions and User Experience. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-granada-2019/\">Read the blog here</a></span></p>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-presenti.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Presenti\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Sara Presenti</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;So, a huge THANKS goes to the organisers and volunteers that made this second edition of WordCamp Granada a complete success.</p>\n<p>We’re so proud to have been part of it and we’re looking forward to coming again next year ;)&#8221;            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"yithemes-interview\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3 profile-name\">\n			                <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/nando-papplardo.jpg\" alt=\"Nando Pappalardo\" class=\"interview-picture\">\n			            <p class=\"interview-name\">Nando Pappalardo</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\n            <div class=\"interview-content\">\n				 &#8220;2019 is coming to an end and this year we have sponsored 20 WordCamps around the world. In five of these, I was also a Speaker (Zaragoza, Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Turin, Catania and Verona) where I shared some of my experiences of maturing during my path of growth, both entrepreneurial and personal.</p>\n<p>Every WordCamp is always a party with so many friends to re-embrace and few days are spent together with laughter, sharing and collaboration. We visit new cities, new nations and sometimes even new continents and it is really nice to see that even between two distant, and apparently very different continents, the people who make up a community have almost identical characteristics: solar, kind, polite and hospitable. This is the WordPress community in the world! I&#8217;m really happy and lucky to be a part of it.            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/sponsoring-twenty-wordcamps-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"YITH themes are back! Proteo theme released! And it’s totally FREE\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/proteo-theme/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/proteo-theme/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 19 Dec 2019 09:00:48 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Premium Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"YITH News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1103461\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:325:\"People who have followed YITH from its very beginning know well that we started out with and were only focused on the development of WordPress themes (that’s why you find the ‘Th’ sound in the word YITH, as it stands for Your Inspiration Themes). We used to sell them on Themeforest marketplace, where we were [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8411:\"<p>People who have followed YITH from its very beginning know well that we started out with and were only focused on the development of WordPress themes (that’s why you find the ‘Th’ sound in the word YITH, as it stands for <strong>Y</strong>our <strong>I</strong>nspiration <strong>T</strong>hemes). We used to sell them on Themeforest marketplace, where we were top authors with some best seller themes (like Maya, Bazar etc…). Until we decided to move our business on to the development of WooCommerce plugins and put the template business on one side.</p>\n<p>But you know what? <em>First love lasts forever</em>.</p>\n<p>That’s why on the pretext of designing a new template for our plugin live demos, we’ve built Proteo, a minimal and elegant e-commerce theme that will gradually replace the default template used in all our live demos (let’s be honest, they really needed a refresh).</p>\n<p>But we couldn’t keep such a beautiful theme on which we worked so hard for ourselves, or limit its use to our live demos only. It would go to waste.</p>\n<p>So, we&#8217;re pretty sure you&#8217;d appreciate that we will share Proteo with the community and release it as a free theme on WordPress.org.<br />\nThe theme will be soon added to the official WordPress.org themes repository and it&#8217;s now available on our <a href=\"https://github.com/yithemes/yith-proteo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Github account</strong></a> for any pull requests and issue reports. We can’t wait to get your opinion and suggestions: we&#8217;ll make this theme the best free solution ever, together!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1103466 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"869\" height=\"804\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335.jpg 869w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-300x278.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-768x711.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-261x241.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-311x288.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-363x336.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image5-e1576674164335-270x250.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 869px) 100vw, 869px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://proteo.yithemes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Live demo &gt;</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/yithemes/yith-proteo/releases/latest/download/yith-proteo.zip\" download=\"yith-proteo.zip\"><strong>Download it &gt;</strong></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Main overview</h2>\n<p>Proteo is a sleek, modern and “Gutenberg-friendly” e-commerce theme.</p>\n<p>Developed with a beautiful UI and a minimal design, it is perfect for each kind of shop. Easy to manage and to customize, Proteo is the best solution if you want a fully-featured e-commerce template to start selling your products with WooCommerce without any specific technical knowledge.</p>\n<p>Use it also for corporate sites or for a blog: there are no limits to what you can do with a beautiful and usable theme like this!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Screenshots</h2>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1103462 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"844\" height=\"833\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804.png 844w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-300x296.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-65x65.png 65w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-768x758.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-261x258.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-311x307.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-363x358.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-270x266.png 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-100x100.png 100w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image1-e1576674274804-80x80.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 844px) 100vw, 844px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1103469 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1103\" height=\"1594\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878.png 1103w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-208x300.png 208w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-709x1024.png 709w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-768x1110.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-1063x1536.png 1063w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-261x377.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-311x449.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-363x525.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image8-e1576674097878-270x390.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1103px) 100vw, 1103px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1103463 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image2-e1576674240379.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"853\" height=\"934\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/image2-e1576674240379.png 853w, https: